Titolo: Crazy Machines

Anno: 2005

Descrizione: Crazy Machines is a puzzle computer game created by German studio FAKT Software GmbH. Crazy Machines based many of its ideas on The Incredible Machine series of games. The player is given a set of mechanical components to construct a Rube Goldberg-style or Heath Robinson-style intricate machine to solve a goal and advance to the next puzzle in the game.
An iOS version of the game was released in 2009.

Genere: Puzzle 

Valutazione: 67
